SECTION 1: THE CIRCULARITY (Documented Finding)
--------------------------------------------------

  M8B c_bound formula:
    c_bound = Delta_DS^(4) * 10^7 * (12/11) * (15/13)
            = 23.796910 * 1e7 * 1.090909 * 1.153846
            = 299,541,524 m/s

  The formula was constructed by asking:
    'What H4 ratios times Delta_DS * 10^7 gives something close to c?'
  Answer: (12/11) * (15/13) = 180/143, giving c_bound within 0.084% of c.

  The Delta_DS itself came from the Bost-Connes sum (M5), which was
  motivated by matching the BSD ratio Omega/R ~ 12.

  Circular path:
    Omega/R ~ 12 [BSD, LMFDB]
