    -> motivates Delta_DS as H4-normalised BSD ratio
    -> gives c_bound via H4 ratios
    -> used to anchor BSD (Omega/R 'explained' by H4)

  This is a known limitation. The math is real. The circularity is real.
  Breaking it requires an INDEPENDENT physical measurement.

